#How to Test the System

1. Submit a New Request (Canvas App Test)

Open the EquipmentRequestApp.

Fill in:

Employee Name

Employee Email

Item Requested

Quantity

Click Submit Request.

Confirm the app navigates to Confirmation Screen.

Go to My Requests and verify the new request appears.

Expected Result:
A new row is created in the EquipmentRequests Dataverse table with Status = Pending.

2. Manager Receives Email Notification

Open the Manager/test email inbox.

Submit another request from the app.

Check for an email titled “New equipment request from <EmployeeName>”.

Expected Result:
A notification email is received within seconds.

3. Manager Approves or Rejects

Open the approval email.

Click Approve → confirm.

OR click Reject → confirm.

Expected Result:
The Dataverse record updates Status to Approved or Rejected, and logs:

ApprovedBy

ApprovedOn

4. Employee Views Updated Status

Open the app → go to My Requests.

Locate the same request.

Expected Result:
Status updates from Pending to Approved or Rejected in real time.
